<div class="aside-image-wrapper">
<figure class="aside-image"><a href="https://thefederalist.com/2019/02/27/no-gun-control-isnt-good-idea-military-officers-say/" title="No, Gun Control Isn’t A Good Idea Because Some Military Officers Say So"><img src="https://thefederalist.com/wp-content/themes/attitude-child/images/pixel.gif" data-lazy-src="https://thefederalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/1024px-thumbnail-998x713.jpg" width="998" height="713" class="attachment-aside-post size-aside-post wp-post-image" alt="No, Gun Control Isn’t A Good Idea Because Some Military Officers Say So" title="No, Gun Control Isn’t A Good Idea Because Some Military Officers Say So" srcset="https://thefederalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/1024px-thumbnail-998x713.jpg 998w, https://thefederalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/1024px-thumbnail-300x214.jpg 300w, https://thefederalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/1024px-thumbnail-768x549.jpg 768w, https://thefederalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/1024px-thumbnail-378x270.jpg 378w, https://thefederalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/1024px-thumbnail-200x143.jpg 200w, https://thefederalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/1024px-thumbnail.jpg 1023w" sizes="(max-width: 998px) 100vw, 998px"><noscript><img width="998" height="713" src="https://thefederalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/1024px-thumbnail-998x713.jpg" class="attachment-aside-post size-aside-post wp-post-image" alt="No, Gun Control Isn’t A Good Idea Because Some Military Officers Say So" title="No, Gun Control Isn’t A Good Idea Because Some Military Officers Say So" srcset="https://thefederalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/1024px-thumbnail-998x713.jpg 998w, https://thefederalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/1024px-thumbnail-300x214.jpg 300w, https://thefederalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/1024px-thumbnail-768x549.jpg 768w, https://thefederalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/1024px-thumbnail-378x270.jpg 378w, https://thefederalist.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/1024px-thumbnail-200x143.jpg 200w, h